description: Binding Omytea-Almighty Git, visibility, and publication contract
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `ORG-SYNC.md` before working. Canonical remote:
`Omytea-Almighty/omytea-personal-console`. Commit only deliberately reviewed paths. The
post-commit transport may push that existing commit, but must never stage,
commit, pull, merge, rebase, force-push, delete refs, change visibility, bypass
hooks, or bypass a curated-public receipt. On any mismatch, preserve the local
commit and report `BLOCKED_*`.
